          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>No Government No Pay Act of 2015</b></p> <p> A Member of Congress may not receive pay, during a government shutdown, equal to the product of the Member's daily rate of pay and the number of 24-hour periods during which the government shutdown is in effect. This prohibition shall apply on and after the convening of the 115th Congress.</p>]]></text>
